~ nova_where
Nova: Where am I?
=> END

~ sage_rules
Sage: Welcome to the BIOS Vault.
Sage: I assess your knowledge with a quiz.
Sage: Three wrong answers, and we settle it in combat.
Sage: Ready?
=> END

~ sage_intro
Sage: Welcome to the BIOS Vault.
Sage: I guard boot protocols.
Sage: Quick check—show me what you’ve learned.
=> END

~ sage_skill_check
do reset_sage_quiz_attempts()
if SceneManager.player_karma == "bad" and SceneManager.deleted_lost_file == true:
	Sage: Your log reads hostile.
	Sage: No quiz. Combat verification only.
	do start_sage_combat()
	=> END
elif SceneManager.player_karma == "bad" and SceneManager.broken_link_fragmented_key == true:
	Sage: You broke the link instead of repairing it.
	Sage: Combat verification only.
	do start_sage_combat()
	=> END
else:
	Sage: Quiz commencing. 15 questions ahead. Answers shuffle each time.
	do shuffle_quiz_questions()
	do show_next_question()
	=> END

