~ quiz_pass
Sage: Nice. You pass.
Sage: Access posture updated to trusted.
do mark_sage_quiz_passed()
=> END

~ quiz_wrong
do register_sage_quiz_fail()
if SceneManager.sage_force_combat == true:
	Sage: Three wrong answers logged.
	Sage: Combat verification begins now.
	do start_sage_combat()
	=> END
else:
	Sage: Not quite.
	Sage: Wrong count: {{SceneManager.sage_quiz_fail_count}} / 3.
	- Try next question.
		do show_next_question()
		=> END
	- Skip to combat.
		do start_sage_combat()
		=> END
